# ğŸ“ LegitCheck â€“ Verify Official Campaign Numbers

LegitCheck is a simple Streamlit app that helps users verify if a phone number is part of an official government or company outreach campaign. Inspired by real-world experiences with legitimate but suspicious-looking communications, the tool aims to provide peace of mind at moments of doubt.

